heart fm ( sinhalese : හා ( ර ) ට එෆ එම ) is a 2008 sri lankan sinhala family drama film directed by senesh dissanaike bandara and produced by soma edirisinghe for eap films .   it stars gayan wickramathillaka , kanchana mendis and sachini ayendra in lead roles along with aruna liyan and mahendra perera .   music co-composed by centigradz and nawarathne gamage .   eap group also celebrated 50th anniversary of e.a.p. films with the production of this film .   it is the 1099th sri lankan film in the sinhala cinema .